  "title": "Business Analyst - DCS - KT",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description / Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3><p><p><em><strong>Work closely with portfolio managers</strong></em> to understand their business requirements, and translating these business requirements to technical requirements, and vice versa</p><p><em><strong>Design, test and implement processes/tools/systems in partnership with in-house IT, risk, and finance teams as well as external software vendors and service providers </strong></em>to support the front-office investment workflow</p><p><em><strong>Develop and write test plans</strong></em> for system, process and product upgrades, as well as <em><strong>participate in the User Acceptance Testing (UAT)</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Develop and maintain user guides and documentations</strong></em> relating to processes/tools/systems implemented for front-office investment workflow</p><p><em><strong>Plan and work with multiple departments in MAS – on implementing road maps of desired front-office workflow, including feature development and upgrades</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Ensure front-office processes and procedures meet internal standards for data integrity, security and auditability</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Monitor, analyse and troubleshoot front-office processes</strong></em> to ensure their smooth functioning. This includes liaising with the in-house IT department as well as external service provider in the troubleshooting and resolution of production issue</p><p><em><strong>Manage project implementations with vendors and service providers, covering procurement and related administrative issues</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Oversee change management to facilitate new product and/or system adoption</strong></em>, including possible re-engineering of workflow and processes.<br /></p><p><br />**Looking for <strong>Business Analyst</strong> with minimum <strong>4</strong> <strong>years of relevant experience</strong> specifically in risk management and/ or trade processing domain / system, including but not limited to Murex, SimCorp Dimension, Blackrock Aladdin, Charles River.<br /></p><p>Work Location : Central<br /></p><p><strong>Singaporeans ONLY.</strong><br /></p><p><em><strong>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Personal data collected will be used for recruitment purposes**</strong></em></p><p></p></p>",
